 점점,,,,말라가고 있으니,,,ㅎㅎ 이럴때 감정 부풀려 줄것이 바로 여행인데,,, ~   오늘도 허리 부여 잡고,,,,간장 달이고 해야하니 ~~ 이런 쓱을 인생,,,ㅎㅎ   12월 첫날,,,좋은하루 만드시고요,, 눈이 온다네요 서울은 첫눈 인가요,,,??   전,,,한의원으로 침 꽂으러 갑니다,,,,              ","images":["http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141130_160/julia0301_1417315363850LKEPx_JPEG/_MG_8946.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141130_187/julia0301_1417315363440Nz6nl_JPEG/_MG_8945.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141130_156/julia0301_1417315362262vcBfi_JPEG/_MG_8926.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141130_45/julia0301_1417315349736KdEmu_JPEG/_MG_8894.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141130_110/julia0301_1417315351041cgdmD_JPEG/_MG_8900.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141130_195/julia0301_1417315352693dd7Rm_JPEG/_MG_8902.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141130_241/julia0301_1417315353777Nj5zf_JPEG/_MG_8906.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141130_234/julia0301_14173153567077DTjD_JPEG/_MG_8909.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141130_144/julia0301_1417315357228yvCDe_JPEG/_MG_8911.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141130_219/julia0301_1417315359195qVGRF_JPEG/_MG_8916.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141130_164/julia0301_141731536030402OF8_JPEG/_MG_8920.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141130_169/julia0301_1417315361449Vb90K_JPEG/_MG_8923.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141130_23/julia0301_1417315361818Edl5g_JPEG/_MG_8925.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141130_16/julia0301_1417315362997h5H7j_JPEG/_MG_8944.JPG?type="],"nickname":"줄리아 황정금요리","id":"줄리아 황정금요리","comment_no":0,"like":0}
